---
title: Mexican Black Bean Fritter & Haloumi Burger with Fries & Smokey Aioli
description: Here we go, it’s another combo that’s going make mouths water and stomachs rumble. Our two stars tonight are black beans
fritters and haloumi in a burger, transforming into a fritter burger that deserves a standing ovation!
